家每日萬三個都秒殺<br />\n代表啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe22eda64d41d77489a62b4fe5f80260ff7bd2f","tid":2430900,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"黨鐵果D唔係要俾錢買架咩??....派???"},{"pid":"d0ec0043b95a72b1a9970029321548640c4c16b3","tid":2430900,"uid":217049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"要求14日例檢<br />\n但減派發量<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb38db172b813c95ac90aeca0fdc6b3c6076599e","tid":2430900,"uid":38744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fe22eda64d41d77489a62b4fe5f80260ff7bd2f","tid":2430900,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"黨鐵果D唔係要俾錢買架咩??....派???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:34:27.000Z","msg":"要嘟八達通，但係唔使扣錢，扣$0"},{"pid":"c68ef8702aeb9085d63415a5b2549e08076abb60","tid":2430900,"uid":33471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c00f34f7e347b44434ea84674ce2d3a78d4661c3","tid":2430900,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210302/7NELA2SXCFEX5IINNCWPCL34P4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR37mSLCpWWhOl99eux8TG4pM_lEPjgmrsNTeJBNsDerIN-n3yQfs_Zaals\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210302%2F7NELA2SXCFEX5IINNCWPCL34P4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR37mSLCpWWhOl99eux8TG4pM_lEPjgmrsNTeJBNsDerIN-n3yQfs_Zaals&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiur32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=535234dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210302%2F7NELA2SXCFEX5IINNCWPCL34P4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%